ZH: 他准许我去参加派对。
EN: He allowed me to attend the party.

ZH: 她准许我使用她的电脑。
EN: She gave me permission to use her computer.

ZH: 我的老板准许我提前下班。
EN: My boss allowed me to leave early.

ZH: 他准许我进入他的办公室。
EN: He permitted me to enter his office.

ZH: 我妈妈准许我去看电影。
EN: My mom let me go watch a movie.

ZH: 老师准许我们使用手机来查资料。
EN: The teacher allowed us to use our phones to look up information.

ZH: 我准许你借我的书。
EN: I give you permission to borrow my book.

ZH: 我们准许你进入我们的社群。
EN: We permit you to join our community.

ZH: 他准许我把这些文件复印一份。
EN: He authorized me to make a copy of these documents.

ZH: 我父母准许我和朋友一起去旅行。
EN: My parents allowed me to go on a trip with my friends.

ZH: 老板准许我们在办公室里吃午饭。
EN: The boss permits us to have lunch in the office.

ZH: 我准许你把这个秘密告诉你的朋友。
EN: I allow you to tell your friend this secret.

ZH: 主人准许我在客厅里玩乐。
EN: The host allows me to play in the living room.

ZH: 老师准许学生们休息一会儿。
EN: The teacher allows the students to take a break for a while.

ZH: 我们准许你使用我们的停车位。
EN: We permit you to use our parking spot.

ZH: 警察准许我通过这个路口。
EN: The police officer allowed me to pass through this intersection.

ZH: 校长准许学生们组织一次校外活动。
EN: The principal permits the students to organize an off-campus activity.

ZH: 我准许你参加这个会议。
EN: I give you permission to attend this meeting.

ZH: 我们准许你在教室里吃零食。
EN: We allow you to eat snacks in the classroom.

ZH: 他准许我在他的花园里拍照。
EN: He allowed me to take pictures in his garden.
